---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Best AI Tools for Real Estate Agents 2025 | AgentAI Guide" description="Curated list of the best AI tools for real estate agents — listing generators, CRM, lead scoring, market analysis.">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Best AI Tools for Real Estate Agents</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-500 mb-10">Curated, tested tools to save you time and close more deals.</p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Listing Description Generators</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-3">AI tools that write MLS-ready property descriptions.</p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
        <li>• <a href="https://listing-description-gen.com" class="text-green-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">ListingDescGen.com</a> — Free, instant</li>
        <li>• ChatGPT with listing prompts</li>
        <li>• Zillow Listing Assistant</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Market Analysis</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-3">AI-powered CMA and market trend tools.</p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
        <li>• HouseCanary</li>
        <li>• Restb.ai</li>
        <li>• PropStream AI</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Lead Generation &amp; CRM</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-3">AI tools to find, score, and nurture leads.</p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
        <li>• SmartZip</li>
        <li>• Offrs</li>
        <li>• Structurely (AI chatbot)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Productivity</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-3">AI assistants to draft emails, contracts, and more.</p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
        <li>• ChatGPT (OpenAI)</li>
        <li>• Claude (Anthropic)</li>
        <li>• Otter.ai (meeting notes)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
